Package: libgrx-fonts
Section: libs
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: 2D graphics library
 A simple 2D graphics library similar to the old Borland Graphics Interface
 (BGI).
 .
 This package contains the fonts used by libgrx.

